    {
      "heading": "Brand Story",
      "subheading": null,
      "body": "Named after the founder's parents Nick and Sally, who have passed. The brand honors their love, support, and belief. Color names are inspired by family members including kids, nieces, and nephews.",
      "image_urls": [],
      "cta": null
    },
    {
      "heading": "Mission",
      "subheading": null,
      "body": "Built with intention to provide high-quality, natural-looking extensions that empower both clients and stylists. It's about confidence, authenticity, and creating something truly special.",
      "image_urls": [],
      "cta": null
    },
    {
      "heading": "Born From Experience, Designed for You",
      "subheading": null,
      "body": "As a stylist and extension wearer, the founder experienced challenges with traditional hand-tied extensions including bulkiness, shedding, unnatural seams, and wasted hair. This led to creating the Active Genius Weft to solve these frustrations.",
      "image_urls": [],
      "cta": null
    },
    {
      "heading": "What makes Nically Hair different?",
