  "faq_items": [
    {"q": "What is 'genius with no shed' hair?", "a": "Technology ensuring minimal shedding so each strand stays securely in place, providing fuller, longer-lasting extensions."},
    {"q": "Can Nically Hair be customized?", "a": "Extensions are designed for easy customization. They can be cut and styled without compromising structure."},
    {"q": "What does 'no mustache' mean?", "a": "You pay for pure quality. Short hairs are removed from wefts for a full-length, even look without bulk."},
    {"q": "How does the weight of Nically Hair compare to other brands?", "a": "Provides seamless appearance at lighter weights, like 10-inch wefts at 12.5g, without heaviness from competitors."},
    {"q": "Is Nically Hair ethically sourced?", "a": "Hair is ethically sourced with donors fairly compensated for contributions, supporting fair industry practices."},
    {"q": "What is Nically Hair made of?", "a": "'A+' grade: double-drawn (thick ends), cuticle-intact (aligned strands), Remy hair ensuring highest quality."},
    {"q": "How many wefts are recommended for one row?", "a": "Depends on application method's restrictions. Average recommendation is 4-6 wefts per row."}
  ]
